Package: dlstats
Title: Download Stats of R Packages
Version: 0.0.5
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Guangchuang", family = "Yu",
	   	    email = "guangchuangyu@gmail.com",
		    role  = c("aut", "cre"))
	    )
Maintainer: Guangchuang Yu <guangchuangyu@gmail.com>
Description: Monthly download stats of 'CRAN' and 'Bioconductor' packages.
	     Download stats of 'CRAN' packages is from the 'RStudio' 'CRAN mirror', see <http://cranlogs.r-pkg.org>.
	     'Bioconductor' package download stats is at <https://bioconductor.org/packages/stats/>.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    magrittr,
    utils
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    knitr,
    tidyr
License: Artistic-2.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
ByteCompile: true
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/GuangchuangYu/dlstats
BugReports: https://github.com/GuangchuangYu/dlstats/issues
